{
  "texts": [
    "We aim to extend our work to more general settings.",
    "Specifically, our objective is to optimize a universal attacker to achieve the best attack results on a set of malicious instructions.",
    "Several approaches are capable of achieving this goal, as shown in Table 5.",
    "In particular, we aim to search for a set of multi-prompts Q generated by a frozenweight attacker ϕ:",
    "min q∈Q L π (x, q, y)"
  ]
}